*Igrali* smo fudbal na plaži. (We played football on the beach.)

*Igrala* je lutka u predstavi. (The doll acted in the play.)

Dečaci su *igrali* u dvorištu. (The boys were playing in the yard.)

*Igrao* je trubu na koncertu. (He played the trumpet at the concert.)

Ona je *igrala* u školskom orkestru. (She played in the school orchestra.)

*Igrali* smo se u parku. (We were playing in the park.)